{"tid":457793,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[挑戰,具整合]一人一間中伏餐廳，我去試食","createTime":"2017-11-04T08:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T05:27:55.000Z","uid":28964,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"9f282c22ddfe9dc24e68196af64ce96364660ec5","tid":457793,"uid":28964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於開到第2個post 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\npost 1 link:<br />\n[挑戰] 一人一間中伏餐廳，我去試食<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/374178/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/374178/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n要大家久等啦...<br />\n係呢個post，將會有post1 嘅整合，排行榜<br />\n仲有萬眾期待嘅各區劣食整合list<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然仲會有第10篇嘅食評啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲<br />\n先比大家睇下10間我已試食嘅餐廳排行榜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/155627_995f8b81ab86d41a43a97b5be9025b60.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F155627_995f8b81ab86d41a43a97b5be9025b60.jpeg&h=4d152fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有post 1 各區劣食統計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/162913_b489b03b826fe72aaee4e011853bd608.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F162913_b489b03b826fe72aaee4e011853bd608.jpeg&h=e6e8a64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/162925_1facac0ed0c73d7a0456ff751ae2fc61.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F162925_1facac0ed0c73d7a0456ff751ae2fc61.jpeg&h=942410fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外為左方便大家睇返之前d食評<br />\n我開左個fb page 等大家易d 追post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%8A%A3%E9%A3%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B-354878384965318/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%258A%25A3%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258E%258B-354878384965318%2F&d=R%2F%2BmfF0kYNTsCQBSFggLuWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9e027eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E5%8A%A3%E9%A3%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B-354878384965318/</a>"},{"pid":"a392f7fc8629fa51f2d50f923a58c8ab785644f9","tid":457793,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c613dcf7c7e627676bf869c32766c2518c36e9","tid":457793,"uid":65612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"lm支持"},{"pid":"73aa91769e6c6bec86cbb1fc0f906b1c96553269","tid":457793,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"16747e5d2ebe8337d3aab3458d38fbf884e6b2f5","tid":457793,"uid":139252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:28:05.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9caa9e4649109e19b40a4ba72eb115e5bfe18100","tid":457793,"uid":42414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:46:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2fef15f5bb31ecbe3933bff4601f91ce1c483dd2","tid":457793,"uid":1304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T19:53:33.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468678c191dbd77138b57010f8d326ab2c511903","tid":457793,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b762911c18fd59d351acc93bd052d4d908c29d68","tid":457793,"uid":25533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T20:14:04.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"aca5ecbf772ea16353b0e12f64d3ccd243af9f6d","tid":457793,"uid":96342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T20:28:23.000Z","msg":"維哥係差左<br />\n但都唔算中伏掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6991cedacddc88825f586f18a4c1c71557f00237","tid":457793,"uid":96342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T20:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>維哥係差左<br />\n但都唔算中伏掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記"},{"pid":"9ef8ed73d53fa06457815ae2b3d0f1042b4c0a3a","tid":457793,"uid":28964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">羅麥豬手 百感交雜</span></strong><br />\n<strong>劣食指數：3/10 (推介人: 大Dick的Dick大)</strong><br />\n<br />\n今日黎到銅鑼灣羅麥記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203319_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203319_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=670dede8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實之前係tko 已經想試呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過tko 實在太多劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直未有機會試呢間<br />\n<br />\n但今日一睇openrice<br />\n發覺tko 果間羅麥記已經執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎真係幾伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我緊係唔可以放過呢個機會啦<br />\n即刻就係剩低果d 分店揀間黎試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一黎到<br />\n發覺人流都好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成間鋪坐得果幾枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢嘅裝修係以傳統懷舊香港冰室做主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203408_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203408_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=82500c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同上次龍鳳冰室唔同<br />\n佢係沿用返舊有嘅冰室特色 冇加到任何現代既元素係入面<br />\n將舊式香港冰室 重新呈現返係你眼前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n餐牌設計方面<br />\n係連登仔最中意嘅多圖少字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203510_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203510_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=88983548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203513_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203513_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=0cb9012b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖文並茂 簡單易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先嗌左個避風塘炒河試一試師傅功架先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203545_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203545_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=f151a0e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炒河黎到熱辣辣岩岩炒起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇落唔算好油膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食落夠穫氣<br />\n牛肉，配料夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n避風塘既辣味同炒河都幾夾 將個河昇華左去另一個層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n河粉冇上次百分百果個咁硬<br />\n口感都算唔錯<br />\n整體可為上品也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住黎個凍奶茶<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203650_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203650_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg&h=01a05ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲落茶味同奶味恰到好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冰唔會太多<br />\n茶濃得黎唔澀 甜度亦都調較得非常好<br />\n亦係上品也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再黎一個芝味牛肉蔥油餅卷<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203713_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203713_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=354e3c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔥油餅岩岩整起<br />\n熱辣辣 又夠脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面d 芝士溶左 流入蔥油餅度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外脆內軟<br />\n再加埋夾住嘅牛肉 口感豐富<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203732_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203732_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg&h=51bc975c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一可以彈嘅係 蔥油餅個粉食落有d 黏口 少少痴牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係印度薄餅果隻咁鬆脆<br />\n但唔太影響整體分數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完呢幾樣 我覺得呢間d 野食真心幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼好過好多間香港既茶記/連鎖快餐店<br />\n唔明點解有人話伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但戲肉就黎啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蜜糖豬手！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個賣相唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/203859_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F203859_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg&h=b0b30967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一食落口就出事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先講口感<br />\n食落皮唔夠淋 有d 韌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n豬手呢，<br />\n就一係食淋<br />\n一係食爽口，彈牙<br />\n佢兩樣都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係中間<br />\n好似食緊橡皮糖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要食食下仲有d 野磨緊條脷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係d 毛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd 豬手好撚多毛！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/204107_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F204107_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg&h=68b3c93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似幫條脷做緊磨沙清潔咁<br />\n估唔到食豬手都有清潔口腔既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講味道<br />\n蜜糖同佢完全唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又鹹又甜<br />\n仲有種黐黐立立既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食食下仲見到有塊藍色野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/204143_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F204143_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg&h=146639fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該係食物包裝d 碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋發現有條頭髮....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/204201_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F204201_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg&h=8782a816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬手仲要細舊 而且多骨少肉<br />\n實屬下品也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n埋單<br />\n$174 兩個人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/204309_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F204309_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg&h=25306aff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真 係希慎呢d 大型商場黎講真心唔算超貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前永發開係tko 賣d 野仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔食豬手 變做雞翼既話呢間其實都幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c250bd3441d4ca7511a30878751610fa33330d92","tid":457793,"uid":28964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"大家可以繼續係呢個post 留你覺得劣既野食<br />\n<br />\n我仲會繼續update 張list<br />\n如果就腳,平平地 我可能都會試食先架<br />\n唔會跟次序試食<br />\n<br />\n有興趣一齊玩試食既朋友都可以留tg 一齊去食劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食劣食都可以係一種樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋利個申先<br />\n每個人口味都唔同 同埋一間餐廳有咁多菜色<br />\n總有啲特別好食/難食<br />\n其實都係睇彩數<br />\n我只係將我當時真實嘅感覺反映出黎<br />\n無意影響大家去呢啲餐廳嘅意慾<br />\n所以大家睇食評既時候無需認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d6c6db397c3dd0632124d6f5b5e0ed0ea67e6b","tid":457793,"uid":111241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1de86ce0ed7afcf8b7af5e023293cda8775a5542","tid":457793,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c398e2ea01c265257c4e18677c1ca24748e0fab1","tid":457793,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"廣東燒味"},{"pid":"f2c77e671265818b5d2277a1587468b3e01d064c","tid":457793,"uid":52702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"荃灣 六合坊 屎中之屎！"},{"pid":"26b4904fa9a82ab37efe9caa8989cc1694a36c0b","tid":457793,"uid":3128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"Support ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e08e51ba6fb45015501e41ba1e94a2551c6cab4","tid":457793,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"如果只能揀一間的話: 灣仔修敦 别天神拉麵"},{"pid":"8089868b99cfc1bb6c55bb54ad1b326d7ab041d8","tid":457793,"uid":146428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"觀塘 古今二"},{"pid":"b4f6e15e96a7d1d729a396713a23f59c9042c129","tid":457793,"uid":112308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"條頭髮捲曲？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da1210e98b6af0aa41f59ef0ba5e82b4d077efc","tid":457793,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63bde0cba02c7c7672d7034d2c5fe31839a5783","tid":457793,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣 勤記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c487f86c8d645b997a61609ba1ca5d085861a730","tid":457793,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銅鑼灣 勤記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個粥狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f40e21ce31fffe9feb52d35e423734139b9896","tid":457793,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"想知龍門點解劣食 <br />\n利申成日食 貪佢夠平抵食"},{"pid":"bf38ead72f63e3ea36eb5e9a6fabd1a3a98da53d","tid":457793,"uid":147800,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T18:25:50.000Z","msg":"慈雲山 陽光茶餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  狗也不屌 啲汁係水咁 仲要有怪味 啲肉又硬又難食 你食得哂成個飯既話 我連續5日食呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568aca1071f0b36c9e9396bc433fccf967b4e353","tid":457793,"uid":96077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T18:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慈雲山 陽光茶餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  狗也不屌 啲汁係水咁 仲要有怪味 啲肉又硬又難食 你食得哂成個飯既話 我連續5日食呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勁多昆蟲 試過外賣凍朱飲完多手望一望 屌成隻小強 大過成隻手指公 巴打唔好用條命較飛"},{"pid":"f9018dbe51765760491a4692abb47cf35fa36096","tid":457793,"uid":63779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T19:19:40.000Z","msg":"觀塘翠屏道翠屏北邨商場地下4號 翠林園餐廳 <br />\n一定要食佢門口POST出黎既碟頭飯，食也不屌。<br />\n麵包好似OK(試狗糧既話唔駛特別試)"},{"pid":"0f3a1e15c14258d5c76948ff7f010d618878ca6f","tid":457793,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T19:47:45.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f9b3ba9e41b00ba227d5d556094d996442bda2","tid":457793,"uid":124574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T20:33:05.000Z","msg":"羅麥記(屯門)個蜜糖豬手真係好難食,芝士撈丁又咸到pk,無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d29f072323db82dfb5303e8d2f7b75d60087228","tid":457793,"uid":29413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"想睇樓主食混亂拉麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba80791785f288b0ddc39e147496cae8fe4c35f5","tid":457793,"uid":15806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"誠意推介觀塘間小時光"},{"pid":"b6efe12525d5f9ba775824e6933548a55122771e","tid":457793,"uid":18624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"西營盤 怡富茶餐廳"},{"pid":"1f77265b2d5aa5a5608ff3095fa8a5f82bc9e7e3","tid":457793,"uid":60552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:34:39.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b3623c940343b3785dac04e4d8ce9898dc1384","tid":457793,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fafb8e851e0b034ec323d1ea281d3c447d4a996d","tid":457793,"uid":147800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>慈雲山 陽光茶餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  狗也不屌 啲汁係水咁 仲要有怪味 啲肉又硬又難食 你食得哂成個飯既話 我連續5日食呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 講岩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢仲做到生意既原因係因為夠平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a466a68b190220afae3964e458d05b037328d6c","tid":457793,"uid":72484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"新田圍南豐<br />\n荔枝角金海棠茶記<br />\n樓主食完覺得好食既話，我叫你做契爺又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece4e82fcb1898e0665d52f7a04bead5b1f74ae2","tid":457793,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b949c19984a29508c403dca5671ec2ce198d9528","tid":457793,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"燉奶佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是旦叫咩都中伏"},{"pid":"bb25377842e1927fc18ce61c2f181882bb3dd993","tid":457793,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"天水圍頌富 80後 90後 好時光 <br />\n牛肉麵甜到糖水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  飲品味道又怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又貴晏就一個餐要成$70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed446d957dbe455b6d7e54371fb2c4c4b5c0ee8","tid":457793,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842a838aa3c17872e845395cb364ad427c4bbc37","tid":457793,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:50:32.000Z","msg":"荔枝角 喜筷客棧 口水雞飯<br />\n口水雞個汁難食到仆街 無味之餘仲有啲酸既配料<br />\n一啲都唔夾 加上雞極之唔新鮮 口感非常差好似煮完雪左好多日咁"},{"pid":"bf368a89511db64a4ee82a73b10b0c2e52df9aba","tid":457793,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"龍門冰室真垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123874109fb1e4bf45cd2ff6efafdf6eda02b276","tid":457793,"uid":71524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"沙田禾輋邨商場入邊既「金時」<br />\n一定要係Lunch時間食"},{"pid":"b3f35cbf953b0e5c1c74e4dcbb6f29feb4d20d32","tid":457793,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"荃灣豚道樂"},{"pid":"bd21412ec6f8cb84f7a5c9f114b8b1593789b668","tid":457793,"uid":69875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荃灣豚道樂</blockquote><br />\n豚道樂同抹茶屋一樣，又係唔算伏不過味道一般同價錢貴，個麵底細到一個女仔食都覺得唔飽，加底要11/12$ ，人手係成日不足，同朋友食嗌兩碗麵等左20分鐘先到，埋單成200-230$ ，同樣價錢我寧願去食一風堂一蘭好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224559dc694383967a97bf8777dd87eeece7893b","tid":457793,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"觀塘 百分百"},{"pid":"4310207e18224e27aa3769c7078e0f28eec4a185","tid":457793,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f79a79538323e98579bd3cb1a091df89645e4f","tid":457793,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"任何一間味皇"},{"pid":"09c4795568207ad9b24c11d9fbd94965e7de8f0e","tid":457793,"uid":45306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"學校canteen計唔計？bu任何一間canteen都歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}